cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.IR. 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning models for understanding paragraphs about processes. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also introduces new neural models, which suggests that it could belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The models are trained on a large dataset, which could also place it in cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper deals with information retrieval and comprehension, which could make it relevant to cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
